5
00:00:46,310 --> 00:00:48,400
那时其他女孩都沉醉于猫王舞步
While other girls were dancing to Elvis...

6
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:49,970
期盼着毕业舞会
and dreaming about prom dates...

7
00:00:50,010 --> 00:00:53,280
而我在读简·奥斯汀 期盼着大学生活
I was reading Jane Austen and dreaming about college.

8
00:00:53,310 --> 00:00:54,980
有一天我父母突然宣布
And then my parents announced...

9
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:57,350
我们要在一个星期内搬去古巴
we were moving to Cuba...in a week.

10
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:03,800
辣身舞 2

11
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:04,800
辣身舞 2
