00:40:46,870 --> 00:40:49,600
怎么样 你决定了吗
So, what did you decide?

562
00:40:51,210 --> 00:40:52,610
我决定参加比赛
I entered the contest.

563
00:40:52,650 --> 00:40:55,670
这很好啊
All right. Good for you.

564
00:40:55,710 --> 00:40:57,680
准备得怎样？
So, how's it going?

565
00:40:57,720 --> 00:41:00,550
挺好的
Oh, great. It's going great.

566
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:04,920
真的吗
Really?

567
00:41:04,960 --> 00:41:07,290
唉 其实不太好
No, it's not.

568
00:41:09,230 --> 00:41:12,220
天啊 我是疯了才觉得我们能行
God, I must have been crazy to think we could do this.

569
00:41:12,260 --> 00:41:13,490
两周后比赛就开始了
It's in two weeks...

570
00:41:13,530 --> 00:41:18,490
每次他前进 我后退
and whenever he pushes, I pull...

571
00:41:18,540 --> 00:41:21,440
我放松自己舞动起来
and I'm flowing, and I'm being free...

572
00:41:21,470 --> 00:41:22,740
我转圈
and I'm making a circle...

573
00:41:22,780 --> 00:41:25,240
也不再僵硬得像熨衣板
and I'm not an ironing board anymore...

574
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:27,250
可还是不行
and it's still not working.

575
00:41:27,280 --> 00:41:30,910
现在他又说 你很害怕
And now he says, "You're afraid."

576
00:41:30,950 --> 00:41:33,480
你害怕吗
Are you?

577
00:41:33,520 --> 00:41:34,950
不怕
No.

578
00:41:36,620 --> 00:41:38,210
那太糟糕了
That's too bad.

579
00:41:42,630 --> 00:41:44,620
过来一下
Come here un momento.

580
00:41:44,660 --> 00:41:46,150
站在这里
Stand right here.

581
00:41:47,930 --> 00:41:50,930
让我看看你的姿势
Let me see your frame.

582
00:41:50,970 --> 00:41:52,340
很好
Good.

583
00:41:55,610 --> 00:41:56,670
手抬高一点
A little pressure.

584
00:42:03,180 --> 00:42:05,340
你从哪学的舞蹈？
So, where'd you learn this?

585
00:42:05,380 --> 00:42:07,680
我父母 他们都是舞者
My parents. They were dancers.

586
00:42:07,720 --> 00:42:09,120
是嘛？
Really?

587
00:42:11,890 --> 00:42:13,360
放松
Relax.

588
00:42:13,390 --> 00:42:14,980
就这样
Yes.

589
00:42:15,030 --> 00:42:16,590
把手放下
Drop your arms.

590
00:42:16,630 --> 00:42:18,650
吸气
Breathe.

591
00:42:21,030 --> 00:42:22,760
试试基本舞步
Now just basic.

592
00:42:25,400 --> 00:42:26,870
很好
Good.

593
00:42:28,710 --> 00:42:32,610
你刚刚为什么说 太糟糕了？
What did you mean when you said, "That's too bad"?

594
00:42:32,650 --> 00:42:34,240
如果你不能克服心中的恐惧
If you can't move through your fear...

595
00:42:34,280 --> 00:42:35,840
不能敞开心扉
and connect with yourself...

596
00:42:35,880 --> 00:42:37,350
那绝对不可能
there's absolutely no way...

597
00:42:37,380 --> 00:42:39,540
和舞伴心有灵犀
you're gonna connect with your partner.

598
00:42:39,590 --> 00:42:41,450
听我说
Listen to me.

599
00:42:41,490 --> 00:42:44,920
我知道让人触碰你的身体
I know that it's scary as hell...

600
00:42:44,960 --> 00:42:46,890
会让你很害怕
to let another person touch that part of you.

601
00:42:46,930 --> 00:42:50,490
但如果做得到 那就值得
But if you do, it's worth it.

602
00:42:51,930 --> 00:42:53,900
现在忘掉我说的话 尽情跳舞吧
Now forget everything I just said and dance.

603
00:44:03,500 --> 00:44:04,900
舞池是你的了
The floor is yours.

604
00:44:06,440 --> 00:44:08,270
回见
I'll see you.

605
00:44:20,120 --> 00:44:21,420
好吧 我承认
OK, I am.

606
00:44:23,620 --> 00:44:24,820
承认什么？
You're what?

607
00:44:27,430 --> 00:44:28,590
我害怕
Afraid.

608
00:44:31,360 --> 00:44:33,960
动作要像水一样灵动
So the movement has to be fluid like the water.

609
00:44:35,600 --> 00:44:38,500
非洲古巴舞 是奴隶的舞蹈
Afro-Cuban dance, it's the dance of slaves.

610
00:44:38,540 --> 00:44:42,340
只有跳舞的时候 他们才能感到自由
When they danced, it was their only time to feel free.

611
00:44:42,370 --> 00:44:47,280
所以他们可以像鸟儿一样
So they could be a bird, you know...

612
00:44:47,310 --> 00:44:50,130
或者跳弗拉明戈舞步
or do a flamenco step

613
00:44:50,130 --> 00:44:52,250
嘲笑他们的主人
and make fun of their owners.

614
00:44:52,280 --> 00:44:53,440
又或者融入大海
Or just be in the sea...

615
00:44:53,490 --> 00:44:56,350
忘记自己被困在远离家园的岛屿上
instead of being stuck on an island away from home.

616
00:44:58,120 --> 00:44:59,810
翩然起舞时
It's a dance

617
00:44:59,810 --> 00:45:02,120
你会成为理想的自己
about being exactly who you want to be in that moment.

618
00:45:07,330 --> 00:45:12,320
你的动作一定要像
It has to feel and look

619
00:45:12,320 --> 00:45:15,440
海浪般自然
as natural as the waves.

620
00:45:15,470 --> 00:45:17,310
潮来
Coming...

621
00:45:17,340 --> 00:45:20,370
潮往
and going.

622
00:45:20,410 --> 00:45:22,140
潮来
Coming...

623
00:45:27,250 --> 00:45:30,550
那时我们在吃晚餐 有人来敲门
We were having dinner, and there was a knock on the door.

624
00:45:30,590 --> 00:45:33,680
两名警察把我父亲带走了
Suddenly two policemen were taking my father away.

625
00:45:33,730 --> 00:45:35,690
谁都可能出卖了我父亲
The traitor could have been anyone.

626
00:45:35,730 --> 00:45:39,690
到处都是巴蒂斯塔的特务
Batista has his spies everywhere.

627
00:45:39,730 --> 00:45:41,260
你知道吗 这就是命
That's the thing, you know?

628
00:45:41,300 --> 00:45:43,300
我父亲没有伤害过任何人
My father never hurt anybody.

629
00:45:43,300 --> 00:45:45,460
他只是一个自由思想者
He was just a free thinker...

630
00:45:45,500 --> 00:45:47,630
但有人不喜欢他的想法
but someone didn't like his thoughts.

631
00:45:50,010 --> 00:45:53,670
我们举行了葬礼 但是没有找到尸体
We had a funeral but we never found his body.

632
00:45:53,710 --> 00:45:56,100
卡洛斯害怕他会成为下一个受害者
Carlos disappeared for a while,

633
00:45:56,100 --> 00:45:57,150
到外面躲了一阵
afraid he would be next...

634
00:45:57,180 --> 00:45:59,240
一天有个女孩抱着孩子来我家
and then this girl shows up with a baby...

635
00:45:59,280 --> 00:46:01,080
说是卡洛斯的 她养不了
says it's his and she cannot afford it...

636
00:46:01,120 --> 00:46:04,750
突然间我肩负起了养活全家的重担
and suddenly I'm in charge of my whole family.

637
00:46:04,790 --> 00:46:07,550
可能这不是你想要的生活
Maybe it's not what you want for yourself...

638
00:46:07,590 --> 00:46:09,580
但是你却做得很好
but you are making a difference.

639
00:46:09,630 --> 00:46:12,690
人们正在进行革命 而我在做什么
There's a revolution out there, and what am I doing?

640
00:46:12,730 --> 00:46:15,500
只是给赃车涂新漆 回家带孩子
Just painting stolen cars and baby-sitting.

641
00:46:15,530 --> 00:46:17,130
不 你维持了全家的生计
No, you're keeping your family alive.

642
00:46:17,170 --> 00:46:19,730
这就是最重要的事
That's the most important thing you could do.

643
00:46:23,480 --> 00:46:27,000
如果我们真的赢得比赛
If we could really win this contest...

644
00:46:27,050 --> 00:46:32,040
说不定我能带家人搬到美国去
maybe I could bring my family to America with us.

645
00:46:39,260 --> 00:46:42,190
你的父母 真是优秀的舞者
Your parents, they're perfect.

646
00:46:44,400 --> 00:46:46,860
他们多么渴望将对方拥入怀中
You see how much they want to be in each other's arms?

647
00:46:48,400 --> 00:46:52,840
我们一起跳舞 我是说真正的舞蹈
For us to dance together, I mean really dance...

648
00:46:52,870 --> 00:46:54,900
就应该是这样
that's how it has to be.

649
00:48:20,860 --> 00:48:22,790
哦 你们继续
Oh, don't let us interrupt you.

650
00:48:22,830 --> 00:48:24,300
不 我们只是…
No, we were just...

651
00:48:24,300 --> 00:48:25,160
嗯 我们看见了
Yeah, we saw.

652
00:48:25,200 --> 00:48:26,860
听着 哈维尔 如果你想点干正事
Listen, we have more stuff in the alley...

653
00:48:26,900 --> 00:48:29,700
巷子里面还有东西要搬
if you want to do something useful, Javier.

654
00:48:31,500 --> 00:48:33,800
我该回家了
I should get home.

655
00:48:50,250 --> 00:48:53,420
想起来回家了？
Thanks for stopping by.

656
00:48:53,460 --> 00:48:55,190
离宵禁还有半个小时呢
It's half an hour before curfew.

657
00:48:55,230 --> 00:48:57,790
你去哪了 参加马戏团了？
What'd you do, join the circus?

658
00:49:00,360 --> 00:49:03,630
你想说你跟詹姆斯出去了？
You're gonna tell me you were out with James?

659
00:49:03,670 --> 00:49:05,260
你是这么跟你妈说的
That's what you told your mother.

660
00:49:05,300 --> 00:49:09,900
我可没把苏西的话告诉她
I never told her what Susie said.

661
00:49:09,940 --> 00:49:11,100
苏西乱说的
Susie was wrong.

662
00:49:14,180 --> 00:49:15,200
好吧
OK.

663
00:49:15,250 --> 00:49:17,410
晚安 爸爸
Good night, Dad.

664
00:49:21,520 --> 00:49:22,650
嗨
Hi.

665
00:49:26,720 --> 00:49:29,090
你要多久才能消气？
How long you gonna be mad at me?

666
00:49:35,470 --> 00:49:36,800
这里的女孩真是
The girls here.

667
00:49:36,830 --> 00:49:38,460
我跟露易丝说我喜欢 简·爱
I told Lois that I like "Jane Eyre"...

668
00:49:38,500 --> 00:49:40,490
她居然问我简·爱演了哪部电影
and she asked me what movie she was in.

669
00:49:44,510 --> 00:49:46,810
对不起 我告了密
I'm really sorry that I told on you.

670
00:49:48,650 --> 00:49:52,010
哈维尔不是那样的人 我错了
And what I said about Javier, I was wrong.

671
00:49:58,160 --> 00:49:59,920
苏西 你要为自己想想
You gotta think for yourself, Suze.

672
00:49:59,960 --> 00:50:02,480
我知道
I know.

673
00:50:02,530 --> 00:50:03,550
我想你了
I miss you.

674
00:50:11,140 --> 00:50:13,870
我好想跟你聊聊最近的事
Well, I've been dying to tell you.

675
00:50:13,910 --> 00:50:15,900
这次你能保密吗
Can you keep a secret this time?

676
00:52:40,120 --> 00:52:41,900
糟糕
Coño.

677
00:52:42,900 --> 00:52:45,300
你要去哪？
¿Adónde tú vas?

678
00:52:45,450 --> 00:52:48,650
今晚可是平安夜 别说你要去工作
Es Nochebuena. XXX dice que vas a ir a trabajar.

679
00:52:48,660 --> 00:52:51,400
我要借你的西装穿
Necesito tu traje.

680
00:52:51,900 --> 00:52:53,600
为什么？
¿Y eso?

681
00:52:54,500 --> 00:52:56,100
我要去参加舞蹈比赛
Voy a una competencia de baile.

682
00:52:59,700 --> 00:53:00,400
在哪儿？
¿Dónde?

683
00:53:00,500 --> 00:53:01,300
豪华俱乐部
En el Palace

684
00:53:02,500 --> 00:53:06,600
你想借西装去巴蒂斯塔最喜欢的地方？
¿Y tú quieres ponerte el traje para ir al lugar favorito de Batista?

685
00:53:06,700 --> 00:53:10,500
不 我要去赢得除夕夜的五千美元大奖
No, lo quiero para ganarme 5000 canas que dan de premio en año nuevo.

686
00:53:10,600 --> 00:53:14,600
当然了 你要去拍那些美国佬的马屁
Sí, claro, meneándole el culo a los americanos.

687
00:53:15,600 --> 00:53:16,500
还有古巴佬的呢
Y a los cubanos, también.

688
00:53:23,130 --> 00:53:27,560
苏西 我和你妈妈有个坏消息要告诉你
Susie, your mother and I have some very disappointing news.

689
00:53:27,600 --> 00:53:29,860
我知道你有多想装饰圣诞树…
Now, I know how you love to decorate the Christmas tree...

690
00:53:29,900 --> 00:53:31,830
唱圣诞歌和看家庭影片…
and sing carols and watch home movies...

691
00:53:31,870 --> 00:53:33,860
但是恐怕今晚…
but I'm afraid tonight...

692
00:53:33,900 --> 00:53:36,130
我们都要去豪华俱乐部
we're all gonna have to go to the Palace.

693
00:53:37,240 --> 00:53:40,300
- 我们都去？ - 是的 苏西 全家人
- All of us?  - Yes, Susie, all of us.

694
00:53:40,340 --> 00:53:42,040
我知道今晚是你和詹姆斯的约会之夜
I know it's your big night with James...

695
00:53:42,080 --> 00:53:44,980
不过 能给老爸留支舞吗
but you think you could save your old man one dance?

696
00:53:45,020 --> 00:53:46,680
什么时候决定的？
When did this happen?

697
00:53:46,720 --> 00:53:48,050
你知道你爸这人的
Well, you know your father.

698
00:53:48,090 --> 00:53:50,110
到处说我们会跳舞
Blabs to everyone we were dancers.

699
00:53:50,150 --> 00:53:52,000
所以菲尔普斯家邀请我们去看
So the Phelpses invited us to

700
00:53:52,000 --> 00:53:52,990
拉丁交际舞大赛
the Latin ballroom contest.

701
00:53:53,020 --> 00:53:54,990
我听说那里的舞跳得很好
Where I hear the dancing is supposed to be pretty good...

702
00:53:55,030 --> 00:53:57,790
但我和你妈妈会去那里挑刺儿
but your mother and I will be looking out for mistakes.

703
00:54:07,200 --> 00:54:10,110
我真想看你父母惊讶的表情
I can't wait to see the looks on your parents' faces.

704
00:54:10,140 --> 00:54:11,510
别刺激我
Don't remind me.

705
00:54:11,540 --> 00:54:13,100
我是不是该责备你
I really should be scolding you...

706
00:54:13,140 --> 00:54:14,870
总是带她出去
for keeping her out till all hours.

707
00:54:14,910 --> 00:54:17,350
不用担心 夫人 我们没有做出格的事
Don't worry, ma'am. We've done nothing you'd disapprove of.

708
00:54:17,380 --> 00:54:19,320
我敢保证
I can promise you that.

709
00:54:31,730 --> 00:54:33,290
谢谢
Thank you.

710
00:54:33,330 --> 00:54:35,030
这边请
Here.

711
00:54:35,070 --> 00:54:37,030
你们两个真般配
You two make a very cute couple.

712
00:54:37,070 --> 00:54:39,730
现在很多美国女孩到这儿来
So many of the girls coming over from the states these days...

713
00:54:39,770 --> 00:54:42,360
都变得 有点儿野了
get a little, you know, wild.

714
00:54:42,410 --> 00:54:45,100
有这样可爱的女儿真是你们的福气
You're lucky to have such lovely daughters.

715
00:54:46,310 --> 00:54:48,340
女士们先生们 圣诞快乐！
Ladies and gentlemen, Merry Christmas!

716
00:54:48,380 --> 00:54:49,370
一会儿
In just a few moments...

717
00:54:49,410 --> 00:54:52,180
今晚的特别节目即将开始
we'll begin this evening's special event.

718
00:54:52,220 --> 00:54:55,080
我们什么时候才能一睹冠军的风采？
So, when do we get to see the championship dancers?

719
00:54:55,120 --> 00:54:56,710
我们可算不上是冠军
We're hardly champions.

720
00:54:56,750 --> 00:54:59,220
你们真谦虚
You're just being modest.

721
00:54:59,260 --> 00:55:00,010
快跳吧
Come on.

722
00:55:00,010 --> 00:55:02,820
我从没看过你们在公共场合跳舞呢
I've never seen you guys dance in public before.

723
00:55:02,860 --> 00:55:05,390
我想如果你丈夫不介意的话…
Actually, I thought if your husband didn't mind...

724
00:55:05,430 --> 00:55:06,620
你和我可以…
you and I might...

725
00:55:07,770 --> 00:55:10,290
詹姆斯…
James...

726
00:55:10,330 --> 00:55:12,300
凯蒂可能想跳舞哦
Maybe Katey would like to dance.

727
00:55:13,600 --> 00:55:15,300
你想跳舞吗？
Would you like to dance?

728
00:55:16,940 --> 00:55:18,970
我想去洗手间
I have to find the ladies' room.

729
00:55:19,010 --> 00:55:20,310
我陪你去吧
I'll escort you.

730
00:55:20,340 --> 00:55:21,570
不用 我自己可以
No, no, I'm fine.

731
00:55:32,120 --> 00:55:34,060
- 你去哪儿了？ - 对不起 我刚…
- Where have you been?  - I'm sorry. I was...

732
00:55:34,090 --> 00:55:36,390
这主意太疯狂了
This was a crazy idea.

733
00:55:36,430 --> 00:55:37,690
不 我们会赢的
No. We're gonna win.

734
00:55:42,930 --> 00:55:44,920
万众期待的时刻到来了
This is the moment you have all been waiting for...

735
00:55:44,970 --> 00:55:47,870
拉丁交际舞大赛正式开始！
the Latin ballroom competition!

736
00:55:47,910 --> 00:55:49,770
前三名的舞者将晋级
Three talented couples will be chosen...

737
00:55:49,810 --> 00:55:51,710
除夕夜的决赛
to compete in the finals on New Year's Eve.

738
00:55:51,740 --> 00:55:54,400
- 太美了！ - 谢谢
- ¡Qué bonita!  - Gracias.

739
00:55:54,450 --> 00:55:55,610
女士们先生们
Senoritas and senores...

740
00:55:55,650 --> 00:55:58,550
欢迎哈瓦那夜晚最璀璨的明星
presenting the brightest star of the Havana night

741
00:55:58,580 --> 00:56:00,980
萝拉 马丁内兹！
Lola Martinez!

742
00:56:07,660 --> 00:56:09,590
凯蒂呢
Where's Katey?

743
00:56:10,760 --> 00:56:12,320
等等吧
Just wait.

744
00:56:17,100 --> 00:56:18,860
哦 我的天啊！
Oh, my God!

