- 我们走吧？ - 好
- Shall we?  - Yeah.

916
01:06:43,230 --> 01:06:45,290
今晚我们将欣赏拉丁交际舞初赛中
Tonight we bring you the three winning couples

917
01:06:45,330 --> 01:06:48,230
晋级的三对舞者
from the Latin ballroom competition.

918
01:07:06,120 --> 01:07:08,450
想跳支舞吗？
Do you want to dance?

919
01:07:20,460 --> 01:07:21,760
你敢
Don't you dare!

920
01:07:48,330 --> 01:07:51,950
新年快乐 女士们先生们
Feliz año nuevo, ladies and gentlemen.

921
01:07:52,000 --> 01:07:57,460
欢迎来到拉丁交际舞业余组决赛现场
Welcome to our Latin ballroom amateur dance contest final.

922
01:08:02,110 --> 01:08:05,940
今晚你们轮流上台表演
You will dance on the stage one couple at a time.

923
01:08:05,980 --> 01:08:10,110
冠军将获得五千美元奖金
Tonight's winning couple will win $5,000.

924
01:08:10,150 --> 01:08:12,770
你们第一个出场
You are up first.

925
01:08:12,820 --> 01:08:17,120
第一组选手是荷赛·维拉尔德先生
Our first couple this evening is Mr. Jose Velarde...

926
01:08:17,150 --> 01:08:19,640
和爱丽丝·梅萨小姐
and Miss lris Mesa!

927
01:08:52,420 --> 01:08:54,150
不要忘了看评委
Don't forget to look at the judges.

928
01:08:54,190 --> 01:08:56,020
其他的就别担心了
Don't worry about the others.

929
01:08:56,060 --> 01:08:59,590
记住 你是黑玫瑰酒吧的舞后
Remember, you're the queen of La Rosa Negra.

930
01:09:00,900 --> 01:09:03,420
今晚表演的最后一组选手是
Our final contestants this evening...

931
01:09:03,470 --> 01:09:07,060
凯蒂·米勒小姐和哈维尔·苏亚雷斯先生
Miss Katey Miller and Mr. Javier Suarez.

932
01:10:06,930 --> 01:10:08,020
抱歉
Sorry!

933
01:10:17,240 --> 01:10:18,800
他拿着枪！
He's got a gun!

934
01:10:18,840 --> 01:10:19,970
不
No!

935
01:10:28,590 --> 01:10:30,920
快走 我会去找你的！
Go! I'll find you!

936
01:10:36,600 --> 01:10:37,700
你承认所有罪行吗？
¿Qué le suela todo?

937
01:10:37,800 --> 01:10:38,900
革命万岁！
¡Viva la revolución!

938
01:10:41,400 --> 01:10:42,100
快跑
Ahora.

939
01:11:01,900 --> 01:11:03,200
- 你疯了吗  - 干嘛？
- ¿Tú ¿estás loco, o qué?  - ¿Qué?

940
01:11:03,210 --> 01:11:04,900
那么多人在场
Toda la gente que estaban ahí…

941
01:11:05,200 --> 01:11:07,300
要是你没有捣乱 我就可以完成任务了
Todo habría salido bien si tú no la hubieras cagado,chico.

942
01:11:07,680 --> 01:11:09,670
对 什么任务 杀人吗？
¿Bien? ¿Bien, que cosa, matar gente?

943
01:11:09,670 --> 01:11:11,240
你要像他们那样做坏事？
¿Cómo lo hacen ellos?

944
01:11:11,250 --> 01:11:12,710
我跟他们不一样
No es lo mismo,

945
01:11:12,710 --> 01:11:15,010
这些人杀了我们的父亲
esa gente que está allí mató a nuestro padre.

946
01:11:15,100 --> 01:11:17,100
你这样做也会杀了别人的父亲
Pero le pudiste haber matado al padre tu también.

947
01:11:20,100 --> 01:11:22,100
你真让我失望
Diego, estaría desilusionado contigo

948
01:11:33,350 --> 01:11:34,820
不
No.

949
01:11:37,400 --> 01:11:40,100
是我对你们两个很失望
estaría desilusionado con los dos

950
01:11:41,700 --> 01:11:42,800
见鬼去吧
¡vete para el carajo!

951
01:11:48,700 --> 01:11:52,500
真奇怪…
Como lo extraño…

952
01:11:53,400 --> 01:11:58,300
有时我真想进父亲的房间去…
A veces pienso que en cualquier momento va a entrar por la puerta

953
01:12:01,400 --> 01:12:02,300
找他的书
Buscando sus libros.

954
01:12:13,400 --> 01:12:15,450
你今晚所做的一切
Lo que hiciste esta noche,

955
01:12:15,450 --> 01:12:18,200
还有你为我们家所做的一切
y todo lo que has hecho por nuestra familia...

956
01:12:20,600 --> 01:12:21,800
谢谢你 弟弟
Gracias, mi hermano.

957
01:12:24,100 --> 01:12:26,100
听着
oye

958
01:12:26,100 --> 01:12:27,500
你是个很糟糕的舞者
Eres tremendo bailarín…

959
01:12:31,600 --> 01:12:33,900
你还是个很糟糕的服务员呢
Y tu tremendo camarero.

960
01:13:23,890 --> 01:13:28,350
革命万岁！
¡Viva la revolucion!

961
01:13:30,330 --> 01:13:32,270
各位贵宾请注意
Attention, all hotel guests.

962
01:13:32,300 --> 01:13:35,200
巴蒂斯塔总统已潜逃出境
President Batista has fled the country.

963
01:13:35,240 --> 01:13:39,470
这里暂时没有危险 请联系前台
There is no immediate danger.Please contact the front desk...

964
01:14:07,240 --> 01:14:08,830
不敢相信真的发生了
I can't believe it's real.

965
01:14:08,870 --> 01:14:11,310
你不想出去和他们一起庆祝吗？
Don't you wanna be out there celebrating?

966
01:14:11,340 --> 01:14:14,830
不 我只想跟你在一起
No. I wanna be right here with you.

967
01:15:22,410 --> 01:15:24,940
我们没有赢得比赛
We didn't win the contest.

968
01:15:24,980 --> 01:15:27,420
对
No.

969
01:15:27,450 --> 01:15:30,440
但鼓励奖也挺不错的
But the consolation prize was pretty good.

970
01:15:37,790 --> 01:15:41,700
我真开心能和你见证这一切
I'm so happy I can see all this with you.

971
01:15:49,740 --> 01:15:52,040
怎么了？
What?

972
01:15:52,080 --> 01:15:54,240
没什么
Nothing.

973
01:15:54,280 --> 01:15:55,900
告诉我
Tell me.

974
01:15:58,510 --> 01:16:00,210
卡洛斯
Carlos...

975
01:16:00,250 --> 01:16:03,810
他总说等革命来了
he always said that when the revolution came...

976
01:16:03,850 --> 01:16:07,050
卡斯特罗会把所有美国公司撵走
Castro will kick out all the Yankee companies.

977
01:16:09,630 --> 01:16:12,060
但你还不确定啊
But you don't really know that.

978
01:16:12,100 --> 01:16:15,330
是啊 但我是说…
No. I'm just saying that...

979
01:16:15,360 --> 01:16:17,490
什么 我可能会被迫离开？
What, that I might have to leave?

980
01:16:17,530 --> 01:16:20,400
有可能
It could happen.

981
01:16:20,440 --> 01:16:21,800
但他们不能那么做
But they wouldn't do that...

982
01:16:21,840 --> 01:16:25,400
革命的思想不就是给人民自由嘛
not if the whole idea is to give people their freedom.

983
01:16:25,440 --> 01:16:27,170
是古巴人民
Cuban people.

984
01:16:28,810 --> 01:16:31,540
好吧 那你就和我们一起走
Well, then, you'll come with us.

985
01:16:31,580 --> 01:16:33,110
我相信我爸可以帮我们
I'm sure my dad can work it out.

986
01:16:33,150 --> 01:16:35,170
那我家人呢？
And my family?

987
01:16:35,220 --> 01:16:36,420
我们会派人去接他们
We'll send for them,

988
01:16:36,420 --> 01:16:37,620
就像我们之前想的那样
just like we were always gonna do.

989
01:16:37,650 --> 01:16:40,310
凯蒂 我想离开是因为巴蒂斯塔的统治
Katey, I wanted to leave because of Batista,

990
01:16:40,310 --> 01:16:41,110
但现在…
but now...

991
01:16:41,160 --> 01:16:42,950
但你又不知道这里会怎样
But you don't know what life will be like here.

992
01:16:42,990 --> 01:16:44,960
我是说 如果情况没有好转呢？
I mean, what if it doesn't get better?

993
01:16:46,660 --> 01:16:48,760
我父亲为古巴革命牺牲了
My father died for this.

994
01:16:48,800 --> 01:16:50,820
我得相信它会好起来
I have to believe it will.

995
01:16:52,500 --> 01:16:54,730
我留在这能有所作为
I can make a difference here.

996
01:16:54,770 --> 01:16:56,500
这是你教给我的
You showed me that.

997
01:16:59,080 --> 01:17:01,870
这是我的祖国 我的家
This is my country.It's my home.

998
01:17:09,890 --> 01:17:11,510
哦 感谢上帝
Oh, thank God.

999
01:17:11,550 --> 01:17:13,180
凯蒂 你还好吗？
Katey, are you OK?

1000
01:17:15,060 --> 01:17:16,790
我们要离开了
We're leaving.

1001
01:17:16,830 --> 01:17:19,190
是的 你爸爸正在安排这事儿
Yeah. Your father's making arrangements.

1002
01:17:39,080 --> 01:17:41,310
把梳子给我
Give me that comb.

1003
01:17:43,490 --> 01:17:45,450
你小时候 当我要帮你梳打结的头发时
When you were little, you used to hide under the bed...

1004
01:17:45,490 --> 01:17:48,460
你会躲到床底下
when I'd try to comb out these knots.

1005
01:17:55,700 --> 01:17:57,690
凯蒂 我一生就爱过你爸一个人
Katey, your father's been the only man in my life...

1006
01:17:57,730 --> 01:18:01,790
所以我不知道跟爱人告别是什么感觉
so I don't know what it's like to say good-bye to someone.

1007
01:18:01,840 --> 01:18:06,070
但是跟我的另一个挚爱…舞蹈 告别时
Saying good-bye to dancing, the other love of my life...

1008
01:18:09,050 --> 01:18:10,570
我的心都碎了
it broke my heart.

1009
01:18:16,650 --> 01:18:18,640
后来你出生了 接着是苏西
Then you were born,and then Susie...

1010
01:18:18,690 --> 01:18:20,780
我太爱你们俩了 我…
and I loved you both so much that l...

1011
01:18:20,820 --> 01:18:22,910
你想说一切都会好起来的
You're saying I'll get over it.

1012
01:18:22,910 --> 01:18:24,550
不 我不是这个意思
No, I'm not. No.

1013
01:18:26,630 --> 01:18:28,790
我是说我知道你很痛苦
No. I'm saying I know you're hurting.

1014
01:18:30,230 --> 01:18:32,100
一切都糟透了
Everything's such a mess.

1015
01:18:34,300 --> 01:18:36,670
你可以选择
You have a choice.

1016
01:18:36,710 --> 01:18:38,540
什么都不做
You can do nothing.

1017
01:18:38,570 --> 01:18:41,910
就躲在床下…
You can hide under the bed...

1018
01:18:41,940 --> 01:18:44,540
或是梳开这些结
Or you can work through the knots.

1019
01:19:07,800 --> 01:19:09,430
我会想你的
I'm gonna miss you.

1020
01:19:14,240 --> 01:19:15,940
我也会想你的
I'm gonna miss you, too.

1021
01:19:17,850 --> 01:19:20,680
我会念着你离去
I am taking you with me.

1022
01:19:20,720 --> 01:19:23,480
我会把你藏在心中
I am keeping you here.

1023
01:19:58,990 --> 01:20:00,790
哈维尔曾说过 跳舞
Javier once said that dancing...

1024
01:20:00,820 --> 01:20:04,190
就是在那一刻成为理想的自己
is about being exactly who you wanna be in that moment.

1025
01:20:04,230 --> 01:20:06,890
和他跳舞时 我意识到我成为了
Dancing with him,I realized I was becoming...

1026
01:20:06,930 --> 01:20:09,760
最想做的自己
exactly the woman I wanted to be.

1027
01:20:09,800 --> 01:20:11,320
我们没有赢得比赛
We didn't win the contest...

1028
01:20:11,370 --> 01:20:13,670
但我们赢到了更重要的奖励
but we did win something more important to us.

1029
01:20:13,700 --> 01:20:15,500
在哈瓦那的最后一晚
On my last night in Havana...

1030
01:20:15,540 --> 01:20:18,700
我们是黑玫瑰酒吧的舞王和舞后
we were king and queen of La Rosa Negra.

1031
01:21:21,140 --> 01:21:23,540
我们不知道何时能再见面
We didn't know when we would see each other again...

1032
01:21:23,570 --> 01:21:26,630
但我知道这不是我们的最后一支舞
but we knew that this wasn't our last dance.
